<h2>Guidelines</h2>
<ul>
 <li>All submissions should be in PDF format and follow the
     <a href="http://www.acm.org/sigs/publications/proceedings-templates">ACM SIG proceedings template</a>.
 <li>Length is limited to 8 pages, but up to four extra pages <i>may</i> be added for a fee.
     <ul>
       <li>We charge $250 each for pages 9 and 10, and $500 each for pages 11 and 12.
     </ul>
 <li>Submissions should represent original, substantive research results.
 <li>At least one author of every accepted paper is required to attend WHIST 2011 in order for the paper to be included in the final proceedings.
  <li>Workshop proceedings will be made available on the web in electronic format.
</ul>
